data.description: Why WAIT for new construction when you can own this IMMACULATE home, located in the highly desired Creek Reserve community TODAY! ** Assumable loan ONLY at 4.75% Interest Rate!!** Offering the popular Aria floorplan with an abundance of magnificent features including the home being a "Smart" home and comes with the added benefit of solar panels, resulting in ZERO electric bills, yup that's right just eliminated one of the usual bills a home comes with. As you approach the home, you'll be greeted by a beautiful front porch, perfect for enjoying your morning coffee or to simply sit back and relax. Step inside and prepare to be amazed by the open and airy floorplan of this 2022-built home. Providing three bedrooms and two bathrooms with a split floor plan that provides the perfect amount of privacy. The kitchen is a chef's true dream, featuring granite countertops, 42-inch cabinetry, a large pantry, and stainless-steel appliances. Whether you're hosting a dinner party or simply enjoying a quiet meal at home, the kitchen is open to both the dining room and living room, making it easy to entertain and interact with guests. The spacious living room provides a comfortable space to relax and unwind. The owner's suite is located on the opposite side of the home from the guest bedrooms, ensuring ample privacy offering a large walk-in closet and an en-suite bathroom with dual sinks, a walk-in shower, a private water closet, and an extra closet for additional storage space. Outside, you will find the large backyard for you and if also your furry friends to enjoy. Additionally, there is a spacious back porch where you can sit back, relax, and enjoy the beautiful Florida weather, scenery, wildlife and breeze. Don't miss out on the opportunity to own this incredible home in the Creek Preserve community. The residence of your dreams in Wimauma! Nestled just outside of Tampa is the location where you’ll find the amazing Creek Preserve community that has all the features you could possibly ever need: Club House, Pool, Tot Lot, Half Basketball Court, Concrete Block Construction. Situated off of US-30 Creek Preserve offers a short commute to Downtown Tampa, St. Petersburg, and Apollo Beach. Not only is it a short trip to the city, but the community is also surrounded by conservation areas and parks. With Little Manatee River State Park just minutes away, there is plenty of opportunity for outdoor adventure such as hiking, canoeing, horseback riding and camping.  Contact us today to schedule a showing and make this house your new home.
